results.description:
Oh my Schedule! I'm a Student is a smart calendar planner. It's a perfect tool for those who want to become more productive and successful.

PLAN A FEW STEPS AHEAD
- Use calendar for quick navigation;
- Create templates to organize courses faster;
- Apply colors to every course;
- Keep control over course duration.

MAKE YOUR STUDY LIFE EASIER TO MANAGE
- Keep track of your homework;
- Leave comments if necessary;
- Add single or regular lessons.

Keep track of your schedule to get the most out of your education process!

